Get back in the car and lock your door.

01:00:34.857 --> 01:00:37.348
- What's his name?
- Andre Bryant.

01:00:37.460 --> 01:00:38.427
Andre.

01:00:42.365 --> 01:00:46.529
<i>Since my pop split, my mom can't even
