01:05:18.341 --> 01:05:21.242
<i>Among the children deported that day
to Birkenau</i>

01:05:21.344 --> 01:05:24.711
<i>was 11-year-old Liliane Berenstein,</i>

01:05:24.814 --> 01:05:28.716
<i>who, before leaving,
